Introduction This is the Public Application Programming Interface of Plealog Bioinformatics Core software.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.core.config
This package contains a utility class that must be used to initialize the Core Library.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.feature
This package contains the components used to model Feature Data.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.feature.utils
This package contains utility classes to handle Features.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.searchresult
This package contains the components used to model a Rich Search Result.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.searchresult.io
This package contains utility classes to read/write SearchResult objects.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.searchresult.utils
This package contains utility classes to handle SearchResults.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.sequence
This package contains the components used to model Biological Sequences.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.sequence.stat
This package contains utilities to compute some statistics about Sequences.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.data.blast.loader.ncbi
This package contains implements a SearchResult loader capable of handling NCBI XML Blast Results.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.data.feature
This package contains concrete implementations of Feature interfaces.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.data.searchresult
This package contains concrete implementations of SearchResult interfaces.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.data.sequence
This package contains concrete implementations of Sequence interfaces.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.io.searchresult.ncbi
This package contains the components used to enable the serialization of NCBI legacy XML results.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.io.searchresult.srnative
This package contains concrete implementations of Native SearchResults serializers.
bzh.plealog.bioinfo.util
This package contains utility classes.

Introduction

This is the Public Application Programming Interface of Plealog Bioinformatics Core software.
